mosquitoes (Japanese Encephalitis vectors), and Anopheles mosquitoes (malaria vectors) if }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid5203216 by}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid7087567\charrsid10102402 
